parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of Takata airbag recall parts can lead to a delay in repairing the vehicle, potentially causing the airbag to deploy improperly or not at all, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: as the issue is related to the unavailability of parts to repair the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Takata airbag inflator can cause the airbag to deploy improperly or not at all, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: Hissing noise from the steering column
particulate matter spewing from the steering column
concern about the airbag's ability to function properly in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the DPS filter can cause the vehicle to shift into first gear without warning, leading to a loss of power and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle shifts into first gear without warning
the vehicle stalls without any indication of a problem
the vehicle experiences sudden loss of power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine stalls without any indication of a problem
the vehicle experiences sudden loss of power
the vehicle stalls while driving or idling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the HPFP can cause the engine to lose power, stall, or fail to start, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle experiences a sudden loss of power
unusual noises or vibrations from the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to a loss of power steering and braking, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The battery light illuminates on the dashboard
unusual noises or vibrations from the electrical system.
